> > Ok, so I did a quick hack and I'm drowning in dmesg WARN_ON() traces
> > with my usual config.
> >
> > This is what I added :
> >
> > diff --git a/mm/slub.c b/mm/slub.c
> > index 6c6d74f..e60dd9e 100644
> > --- a/mm/slub.c
> > +++ b/mm/slub.c
> > @@ -20,6 +20,7 @@
